---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';

---

<Layout title="Changelog 更新日志 | 通俗版 Claude Code 文档" description="Claude Code 版本更新记录" pathname="/docs/en/changelog">
	<article class="space-y-8">
		<header class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em]" style="color: var(--muted);">Getting started</p>
			<h1 class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl font-semibold">Changelog 更新日志</h1>
			<p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8">查看 Claude Code 的最新版本更新和功能变化。</p>
			<p class="mt-4 max-w-4xl leading-8" style="color: var(--muted);">
				原页来源：
				<a href="https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="underline decoration-dotted underline-offset-4">GitHub CHANGELOG.md</a>
			</p>
		</header>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">一句人话</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p>更新日志在 GitHub 上，记录了每个版本的新功能、修复的问题、breaking changes。</p>
				<p>建议每次更新前看看，了解有什么变化。</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">怎么看更新日志</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8" style="color: var(--muted);">
				<p>访问 <a href="https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="underline decoration-dotted underline-offset-4">GitHub CHANGELOG.md</a> 查看完整更新历史。</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</article>
</Layout>
